reviewText: Great talant! Unfortunately I can't speak German, so I can't understand what Mr. Latsabidze is saying, but I do understand his masterful playing and the gift projecting from his eyes! His technique and colors are just unbelievable! It's worth to buy and add to your classical music dvd collection.

Wonderful music, beautiful performance! Too bad dvd has no chapters or track listings! Still, it's worth to buy it and watch his masterful performance of Liszt and Chopin! Great Documentary snippets made by Austrian TV chanel. Enjoyed!
